{
  "texts": [
    "To be precise,h i,l Std ∈ R dStd, h i,l Tch ∈ R dTch, U l Std ∈ R d low ×dStd, U l Tch ∈ R d low ×dTch, d low << d Std ≤ d Tch,where d Tch & d Std denote the embedding (hidden) dimension of the teacher and the student model respectively.",
    "Usually, the dimension d low of the projected space is chosen to be small, 128 in our experiments.",
    "Results on Encoder and Decoder LLMsWe report performance on encoder tasks using GLUE [35] with BERT base as the teacher model Φ Tch.",
    "For decoder LLMs, we use Santacoder [1] and Codellama7B [29] on a python coding task using bigcode/the-stack data [19].",
    "We report performance of the sub-transformer models at the end of stage s = 2."
  ]
}